Title: Biogenesis (1)
Plot: Two scientists confer about each of their metal objects that were found in Africa and they theorize that the objects are pieces of a puzzle which could be undeniable proof that human, plant, and animal life did not originate on this planet. When one of the scientists is killed and the objects are stolen, the agents investigate and Mulder begins to experience severe neurological pain caused by the objects.
GuestStars: Sheila Tousey, Warren Sweeney, Chet Grissom, Marty Zagon, Samuel Kwaku Minta, Ayo Adeyemi, Benjamin Ochieng, Murray Rubinstein, Michael Chinyamurindi, Michael Ensign
